    "en": {
      "title": "Fares for both increase today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Fares for both have been increased today (08). Accordingly, the Railway fare hike notification was released today (08).",
        "However, the Railway Department has announced that the fare increase will be implemented from the coming 11th Monday.",
        "In this case, the rental charges for vehicles hired from Katunayake Bandaranaike International Airport have also been increased.",
        "76,300 rupees to Kangesanthurai and 73 thousand rupees to Jaffna from the airport."
      ],
